ay (30 x 40 cm) with aluminium foil and set aside."},{"content":"Thread marinated pork onto skewers (approx. 3 pieces per skewer) and place onto prepared tray. Grill for 18-25 minutes, turning occasionally, or until pork is cooked through, then serve."}],"hintsAndTricks":["You can use either pork fillet or diced pork shoulder in this recipe."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","7h 25m","12 portions"]}